lga_name.title: Local Government Area Name
lga_name.description: Name of the local government area

number_of_hospitals_health.title: Number of hospitals/health services
number_of_hospitals_health.description: The number of hospitals and health service campuses located within the LGA. Includes both public and private hospitals.

number_of_schools.title: Number of schools
number_of_schools.description: The number of schools located in the LGA. This item includes government private and Catholic primary and secondary schools. It also includes schools for children with special needs.

perc_born_overseas.title: %Born overseas
perc_born_overseas.description: The percentage of the population who were born overseas.
